  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7104351">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7104351/" class="title-link">被忽略的“丑”</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7104351"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/longs/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1719574-8.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/longs/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">龙九天</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-09-19"
      class="main-meta">2014-09-19 07:19:19</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7104351_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  丑是一种社会现象，与美相反。认识美大概是人的天性，原始社会人们制作的陶器上会画上鱼刺、人面一类的花纹，可看成人类追求美的最早阶段。随着人类的发展和文明的进步，人们越来越认识到美，并追求美，进而有了“审美”。可是，长久以来，一直被人们忽略的是“审丑”，丑一直...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7104351/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">11有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7104351_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7104351_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
